Plans for 0.2.0
===============

  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  ? = Questionable

  [W] Implement spell-checking using PyEnchant
        [D] Script to test PyEnchant installation
        [W] Glade files for dialogs (Gedit!)
        [D] langlib for iso-codes
        [W] config entries
        [W] Language selection dialog
        [W] Spell-check dialog (wxSpellCheckerDialog.py!)
        [W] Spell-checker delegate
        [W] Menu entry visibility
        [ ] Test error handling
        [ ] Test unicode handling
        [ ] Ensure that PyEnchant is easily installable (dependecies!)
        [W] Revise README file (PyEnchant & iso-codes)
        [ ] Revise Website (PyEnchant & iso-codes)
  [W] Garbage collect destructed GObjects
  [W] Always copy.deepcopy nested lists instead of [:]
  [W] Revise terminology: project = main document + translation document
  [W] Revise terminology: open translation instead of importing
  [?] Assign Ctrl + arrow keys for moving to edit an adjacent cell
  [W] Automate delegate listings
  [ ] Make config module use global variables for easy access
  [D] Add a text parser
  [?] Redesign the undo/redo system
  [ ] Make fallback encodings be a list
  [ ] Add default and fallbck encoding selection to preferences dialog
  [ ] Update Finnish translation


