New in PyGTK 2.8
================

  http://live.gnome.org/PyGTK/WhatsNew28
  http://www.pygtk.org/pygtk2reference/pygtk-ref-changelog.html
 
  - gobject.GObject: deprecation warning for gobject.type_register(Class)
  - gobject.GObject: widget.props.property_name notation
  - gtk.FileChooser: stock overwrite dialog with set_do_overwrite
  - gtk.AboutDialog: wrap license with set_wrap_license
